ompany known previously as chase manhattan international limited was founded on september   in august  the bank announced plans to construct a new european headquarters at canary wharf london these plans were subsequently suspended in december  when the bank announced the purchase of a nearby existing office tower at  bank street for use as the european headquarters of its investment bank  bank street had originally been designated as the european headquarters of enron and was subsequently used as the headquarters of lehman brothers international europe the regional office is in london with offices in bournemouth glasgow and edinburgh for asset management private banking and investment financial dataedit financial data in  millions  year            revenue             net income            assets            employees            asset  liability assetliability ratio net income jpmorgan chase was the biggest bank at the end of  as an individual bank not including subsidiaries operationsedit earlier in  the company announced that by the use of supercomputers the time taken to assess risk had been greatly reduced from arriving at a conclusion within hours to what is now minutes the banking corporation uses for this calculation fieldprogrammable gate array technology historyedit the bank began operations in japan in  in australia during the later part of the nineteenth century and in indonesia during the early s an office of the equitable eastern banking corporation one of jp morgans predecessors opened a branch in china in  and chase national bank was established there in  the bank has operated in saudi arabia and india since the s chase manhattan bank opened an office in korea in  the firms presence in greece dates to  an office of jpmorgan was opened in taiwan in  in russia soviet union in  and nordic operations began during the same year operations in poland began in  lobbyingedit jp morgan chases pac and its employees contributed  million to federal campaigns in  an